Functional Test Suite
ID: TC-01
Feature: Onboarding
Scenario: Register with an already existing email.
Expected Human Outcome: System should show a clear Email already in use message instead of a server error.

ID: TC-02
Feature: Payments
Scenario: Use a declined card on the Summit tier.
Expected Human Outcome: User should be kept on the payment page with a clear Payment Failed notification.

ID: TC-03
Feature: AI Logic
Scenario: Ask the AI Receptionist a question outside its training scope.
Expected Human Outcome: The AI should gracefully handle the query or provide a fallback option instead of crashing.

ID: TC-04
Feature: Data Sync
Scenario: Edit a product in Shopify and check the SaaS dashboard.
Expected Human Outcome: The change should reflect within 60 seconds without a manual page refresh.

ID: TC-05
Feature: Responsive Design
Scenario: Open the BI Dashboard on an iPhone 13.
Expected Human Outcome: Charts should resize and stack vertically so they remain readable and clickable.
